                  <interp inst="t18201028-119-crimeloc650" type="placeName" value="Wheeler-street, Spitalfields"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18201028-119-crimeloc650" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18201028-119-off646 t18201028-119-crimeloc650"></join>. Having missed property, I watched in the silk room, he was working in the loft where the silk was. On the 25th of October, about half-past ten o'clock in the morning, I saw him put this silk in his hat, and put his hat on, he then went on working. I followed him down stairs, and secured him with it in his hat. He was apprehended.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18201028-119-person1173">
